=== Cultural properties ===
=== Registered cultural properties of Hyogo Prefecture ===
* Tangible cultural properties
** Yabu Shrine, 5 structures (buildings) - registered March 5, 2010 (Heisei 22)<ref>{{Cite web|和書|format=PDF |url=http://www.hyogo-c.ed.jp/~shabun-bo/gyouseisituhp/top/29kentouroku.pdf |title=List of prefecturally registered cultural properties |website=Hyogo Prefectural Education and Training Institute |accessdate=2020-01-13}}</ref>.
*** Main hall - built in the late Edo period.
*** Worship hall - built in the late Edo period.
*** Main hall of Sessha Yamanokuchi Shrine - built in the late Edo period.
*** Main hall of Sessha Gosha Shrine - built in the late Edo period.

=== Yabu City designated cultural properties ===
* Tangible cultural properties
** Stone hōkyōintō pagoda - designated May 18, 1977 (Showa 52)<ref>Explanation board for the stone hōkyōintō pagoda.</ref>.
* Intangible folk cultural properties
** Oshiri Festival

=== Access ===
* Rail / bus
** About 2 km on foot from {{ill|lt=Yabu Station|Q871175|WD=Q871175|1=Yabu Station}} on the JR {{ill|lt=San'in Main Line|Q1135170|WD=Q1135170|1=San'in Main Line}}
** From JR San'in Main Line Yabu Station, take {{ill|lt=Zentan Bus|Q11389110|WD=Q11389110|1=Zentan Bus}} bound for "Yōka Station" and get off at "Yabu Myojin"
** From JR San'in Main Line {{ill|lt=Yōka Station|Q870988|WD=Q870988|1=Yōka Station}}, take Zentan Bus bound for "Wadayama / Yamaguchi" and get off at "Yabu Myojin"
* Roads
** About 1 hour from {{ill|lt=Fukuchiyama Interchange|Q11594317|WD=Q11594317|lt=Fukuchiyama IC|1=Fukuchiyama interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Maizuru-Wakasa Expressway|Q11613730|WD=Q11613730|1=Maizuru-Wakasa Expressway}}
** About 20 minutes from the Asago-side exit of the {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Tōen Tunnel Toll Road|1=UNKNOWN}}
** About 15 minutes from {{ill|lt=Wadayama Interchange|Q10921611|WD=Q10921611|lt=Wadayama IC|1=Wadayama interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Bantan Renraku Road|Q11498699|WD=Q11498699|1=Bantan Renraku Road}}
** About 5 minutes from {{ill|lt=Michi-no-Eki Yabu|Q11640978|WD=Q11640978|1=Roadside station Yabu}} and {{ill|lt=Michi-no-Eki Tajima Rakuza|Q11641146|WD=Q11641146|1=Roadside station Tajima-rakuza}}

